[SPEAKER_01]: May, we can do May 17th.

437
00:35:52,159 --> 00:35:52,559
[SPEAKER_05]: Oh, good.

438
00:35:52,599 --> 00:35:52,859
[SPEAKER_05]: Okay.

439
00:35:52,879 --> 00:35:53,759
[SPEAKER_05]: Yeah, I can do that.

440
00:35:53,779 --> 00:35:53,940
[SPEAKER_05]: Yeah.

441
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:54,640
[SPEAKER_01]: That's fine.

442
